<section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 bg-warm border-b border-gold-light/20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif-display mb-12 text-center animate-on-scroll font-playfair text-charcoal">Investor Experiences</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
            <div class="p-8 rounded-sm bg-white/40 border border-gold-light/30 hover:border-gold-rich/40 hover:bg-white/60 transition-all duration-300 animate-on-scroll cursor-default shadow-sm">
                <div class="mb-6 text-gold-medium/40">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" class="w-8 h-8"><path d="M11.192 15.757c0-.88-.23-1.618-.69-2.217-.326-.412-.768-.736-1.325-.972V12.5c0-1.584.655-2.826 1.966-3.728l-1.326-1.58c-1.339.891-2.217 1.993-2.634 3.31-.383 1.205-.291 2.47-.291 4.296h4.3zM18.192 15.757c0-.88-.23-1.618-.69-2.217-.326-.412-.768-.736-1.325-.972V12.5c0-1.584.655-2.826 1.966-3.728l-1.326-1.58c-1.339.891-2.217 1.993-2.634 3.31-.383 1.205-.291 2.47-.291 4.296h4.3z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <p class="text-charcoal/80 font-light italic mb-8 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    "My CPA was skeptical until she reviewed the structure. The combination of the ITC and depreciation provided an immediate reduction in my liability that I couldn't find elsewhere."
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gold-light/20 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-serif-display text-gold-rich font-bold">RM</div>
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-charcoal">Robert M.</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-charcoal/40 font-medium">Orthopedic Surgeon</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
            <div class="p-8 rounded-sm bg-white/40 border border-gold-light/30 hover:border-gold-rich/40 hover:bg-white/60 transition-all duration-300 animate-on-scroll cursor-default shadow-sm" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
                <div class="mb-6 text-gold-medium/40">
                   <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" class="w-8 h-8"><path d="M11.192 15.757c0-.88-.23-1.618-.69-2.217-.326-.412-.768-.736-1.325-.972V12.5c0-1.584.655-2.826 1.966-3.728l-1.326-1.58c-1.339.891-2.217 1.993-2.634 3.31-.383 1.205-.291 2.47-.291 4.296h4.3zM18.192 15.757c0-.88-.23-1.618-.69-2.217-.326-.412-.768-.736-1.325-.972V12.5c0-1.584.655-2.826 1.966-3.728l-1.326-1.58c-1.339.891-2.217 1.993-2.634 3.31-.383 1.205-.291 2.47-.291 4.296h4.3z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <p class="text-charcoal/80 font-light italic mb-8 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    "I needed a strategy to offset a capital gain event from a business exit. The Solaris team moved quickly to allocate funds before year-end."
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gold-light/20 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-serif-display text-gold-rich font-bold">DK</div>
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-charcoal">David K.</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-charcoal/40 font-medium">Tech Entrepreneur</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

             <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
             <div class="p-8 rounded-sm bg-white/40 border border-gold-light/30 hover:border-gold-rich/40 hover:bg-white/60 transition-all duration-300 animate-on-scroll cursor-default shadow-sm" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
                <div class="mb-6 text-gold-medium/40">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" class="w-8 h-8"><path d="M11.192 15.757c0-.88-.23-1.618-.69-2.217-.326-.412-.768-.736-1.325-.972V12.5c0-1.584.655-2.826 1.966-3.728l-1.326-1.58c-1.339.891-2.217 1.993-2.634 3.31-.383 1.205-.291 2.47-.291 4.296h4.3zM18.192 15.757c0-.88-.23-1.618-.69-2.217-.326-.412-.768-.736-1.325-.972V12.5c0-1.584.655-2.826 1.966-3.728l-1.326-1.58c-1.339.891-2.217 1.993-2.634 3.31-.383 1.205-.291 2.47-.291 4.296h4.3z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <p class="text-charcoal/80 font-light italic mb-8 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    "Legitimate, transparent, and efficient. The K-1 arrived on time, and the cash flow distributions have exceeded the initial conservative projections."
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gold-light/20 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-serif-display text-gold-rich font-bold">SL</div>
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-charcoal">Sarah L.</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-charcoal/40 font-medium">Family Office Director</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

